---
import FormattedDate from "@/components/FormattedDate.astro";
---

<ul>
    <li class="py-2">
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2026-03-01")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                Our paper <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.10436">"Tree Bandits for Generative Bayes"</a> has been accepted to appear in the <em>Journal of the American Statistical Association</em>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2025-10-20")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                I am presenting my recent work on Bayesian nonparametric conditional quantile regression (IQ-BART) at the Booth Econometrics &amp; Statistics student seminar.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>


        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2025-07-08")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                We posted a preprint for our new method <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2507.04168">IQ-BART</a>, which employs a forest prior over the conditional quantile function. This allows for uncertainty quantification about a nonparametric conditional model.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2025-06-25")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                I'll be at <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://bnp14.org">BNP14</a>, presenting about accelerating likelihood-free inference with a tree-based reinforcement learning method.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2025-02-27")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    Our new preprint on <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2502.19231">AI-Powered Bayesian Inference</a> is now available, in which we develop a framework to leverage AI systems to elicit informative priors for Bayesian statistical analyses.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2024-08-18")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    Check out a preprint of my latest work <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2408.08990">"Adaptive Uncertainty Quantification for Generative AI" </a> with Jungeum Kim and Veronika Ročková, where we obtain locally adaptive conformal prediction sets in settings where training data may not be available, like modern large-scale generative models.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2024-07-18")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    I gave an oral presentation at <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline"  href="https://ic2s2-2024.org/">IC2S2</a> in Philadelphia on representations of ideology in large language models.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2024-05-14")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                I received the <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline"  href="https://stat.uchicago.edu/news/article/congratulations-to-our-consulting-award-recipients-for-2023-24/">Senior Consultant Award</a> for the the 2023&ndash;2024 academic year, as well as the <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline"  href="https://stat.uchicago.edu/news/article/congratulations-to-our-consulting-award-recipients-for-2023-24/">Consulting Cup Award</a> for Spring 2024.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>


        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2024-04-16")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    I posted a <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2404.10436">preprint</a> with Jungeum Kim and Veronika Ročková on accelerating approximate Bayesian computation using a tree-based partitioning.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2024-02-05")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    I am giving a <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href=https://cam.uchicago.edu/events/event/1829/?past=y">presentation</a> in the CAM &amp; Stats student seminar on reinforcement learning techniques for approximate Bayesian computation.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2023-12-18")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    My work with Aaron Schein was presented at the NeurIPS workshop "I Can't Believe it's not Better" in New Orleans, LA. Check out a preprint <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline" href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2312.09203">here</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2023-11-09")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                    I presented my work on eliciting ideological scales from large language models at the New Directions in Text as Data conference (TADA) in Amherst, MA.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
        </article>
        <article class="flex flex-row pb-2">
            <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 min-w-[6rem]">
                <FormattedDate date={new Date("2023-05-16")}/>
            </div>
            <div class="pl-4">
                <p class="max-w-64">
                I received the <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline"  href="https://stat.uchicago.edu/news/article/our-2022-23-consulting-and-senior-consultant-award-winners/">Senior Consultant Award</a> for the the 2022&ndash;2023 academic year, as well as the <a class="text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-500 hover:underline"  href="https://stat.uchicago.edu/news/article/the-winter-consulting-cup-award/">Consulting Cup Award</a> for Winter 2023.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>

        <!-- <article class="flex flex-row pb-2"> -->
        <!--     <div class="font-medium text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 w-32"> -->
        <!--         <FormattedDate date={new Date("2023-11-09")}/> -->
        <!--     </div> -->
        <!--     <div class="pl-4"> -->
        <!--         <p class="max-w-none"> -->
        <!--        More to come -->
        <!--         </p> -->
        <!--     </div> -->
        <!-- </article> -->
    </li>
</ul>
